elements.name: List all the Samsung phones with specification as Camera Resolution - 20 MP and above, Model Year – 2023 & Price Range between £50 - £100

steps.name: I am on the Amazon home page
I click on hamburger menu bar
I click on Electronics And Computers
I click on Phones and Accessories
I click on Mobile Phones & Smartphones
I select Camera Resolution as "20 MP & above"
I select Price Range between £"200" to £"250"
I can see list of products matching search criteria
